## Features

**Buyers**
- Register and log in
- Browse products by category, search, and filter
- View product details with images and reviews
- Add to cart and wishlist
- Apply coupon codes at checkout
- Track orders with live status steps
- Chat directly with sellers in real time
- Access Nesty, the AI support assistant

**Sellers**
- Register with store name and business details
- Manage products with multiple image uploads
- View and update order statuses
- Create and manage discount coupons
- Monitor revenue and sales through analytics charts
- Manage inventory stock levels
- Chat with buyers in real time

**Admin**
- View all users, sellers, and orders
- Approve or suspend seller accounts
- Monitor platform-wide activity

**AI Assistant (Nesty)**
- Powered by Claude (Anthropic API)
- Answers questions about orders, returns, delivery, payments
- Responds in English or Urdu
- Available 24/7 as a floating chat bubble

