## Real-time Chat

MarketNest uses Socket.IO for real-time buyer-seller messaging. Both users join a shared room identified by their sorted user IDs. Messages are delivered instantly and also saved to the database for persistence.

---

## Deployment

For production deployment on AWS:

- **Frontend** — AWS Amplify (auto-deploys from GitHub)
- **Backend** — AWS Elastic Beanstalk (Node.js platform)
- **Database** — AWS RDS PostgreSQL
- **File uploads** — AWS S3

Update `FRONTEND_URL` in your backend environment variables to your Amplify domain, and update `VITE_API_URL` in your frontend to your Elastic Beanstalk URL before deploying.

